<h1>
<span> <a href="//slashdot.org/story/24/11/12/2130236/microsoft-edge-is-trying-to-forcefully-get-your-chrome-tabs-again">Microsoft Edge Is Trying To Forcefully Get Your Chrome Tabs Again</a> <span><a href="https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294454/microsoft-edge-chrome-tabs-prompt-trick" title="External link - https://www.theverge.com/2024/11/12/24294454/microsoft-edge-chrome-tabs-prompt-trick" target="_blank"> (theverge.com) </a></span></span>
<span><a href="//slashdot.org/story/24/11/12/2130236/microsoft-edge-is-trying-to-forcefully-get-your-chrome-tabs-again#comments">39</a></span>
